Mirror operations: sync, restore

Usage: sleet mirror <COMMAND>

Commands:
  sync     Run a single sync pass for one (database, target), regardless of the target's mode; prunes afterward when retention is set
  restore  Copy one restore point's closure from a backup into an empty destination root and commit it
  help     Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -h, --help  Print help
